      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 7908091968475454802}
    - target: {fileID: 5122842465899161861, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "Cuckoo Flower\n\nThe cuckoo and the cuckoo flower,\nThe one as sad
        as the other is splendid\nIt must be the blood from the birds mouth\nWhich
        has dripped to become the flower on the branches.\n\n\u2014 Cheng Yanxiong"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5122842465899161861, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_TextStyleHashCode
      value: -1183493901
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5431834928911583797, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Sprite
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8ddfc901fb5dc4540b9e1cd3b71acf22, type: 3}
    - target: {fileID: 5488519469664222319, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: Rhododendron honey is used by the Gurung People of the Himalayas as
        Medicine and a narcotic, but is known all over Eurasia, famous for incapacitating
        Xenophon's Greek army
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5488519469664222319, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_TextStyleHashCode
      value: -1183493901
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5902464882853280731, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: instanceId
      value: ca8f54ec-f72c-4fa0-8b8d-ab9dffbc1765
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5956918439778082410, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: Cuckoos sing tirelessly. Compared to other birds who have a specific
        song, or sing at certain times of day, cuckoos never stop, going all day
        and night.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5956918439778082410, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_TextStyleHashCode
      value: -1183493901
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5956918439778082416, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: This blood stains the flower petals, giving them their deep reds and
        purples.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5956918439778082416, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_TextStyleHashCode
      value: -1183493901
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6181259333930047258, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: GsplatAsset
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 4599839170941234424, guid: e2bda0455c83e554b9326651ad7568d3, type: 3}
    - target: {fileID: 6181259333930047258, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_assetGuid
      value: e2bda0455c83e554b9326651ad7568d3
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6350206799883668920, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_SizeDelta.x
      value: 1166
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6350206799883668920, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_SizeDelta.y
      value: 1357.97
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6835627233580907840, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Sprite
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 21300000, guid: aa75b190b0538ec4492cfea33fb139bf, type: 3}
    - target: {fileID: 7173199714940506848, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "In Chinese the cuckoo and the rhododendron share one name, d\xF9ju\u0101n
        (\u675C\u9E43), tracing back to Duyu, an early and half-mythical emperor
        of Shu."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7173199714940506848, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_TextStyleHashCode
      value: -1183493901
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7417057368276200879, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Sprite
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7fb56e12650cd464ebbaf9af5a4a12e4, type: 3}
    - target: {fileID: 8810918796485297829, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Sprite
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 2d9482c07ee8c4649a0bdee532243611, type: 3}
    - target: {fileID: 9161542878112791018, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: On his death he became the cuckoo, whose cry each spring calls the farmers
        back to their fields. It is said the bird sings until its mouth bleeds.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 9161542878112791018, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_TextStyleHashCode
      value: -1183493901
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
